<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: url('/dogpic.jpg') no-repeat center center fixed;
            background-size: cover;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1, p {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .back-home-btn {
            display: block;
            width: 200px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

            .back-home-btn:hover {
                background-color: #45a049;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <p>
            We are Ziv Faigenboim and Yonatan Guetta, two students of software engineering in our third year of studies.
            Together, we have developed a pet shop where you can find a wide collection of products for any animal you have as a pet.
            Our shop allows you to browse through various products, view prices, add items to your cart, and enjoy many more options.
            With a passion for both technology and animals, we aim to provide a seamless shopping experience for all pet lovers.
        </p>
        <button class="back-home-btn" onclick="window.location.href='/Home/Index'">Back Home</button>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
